{"tid":1538292,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實撤回唔撤回本來就係五大訴求最廢既一項","createTime":"2019-09-04T06:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:16:32.000Z","uid":205394,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"577c7c65da7d0141a0a43f506f77f65a8e367354","tid":1538292,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:47:46.000Z","msg":"五大訴求入面最廢既本來就係撤回送中<br />\n<br />\n本來暫緩又好，壽終正寢又好<br />\n呢條條例本來就廢撚左<br />\n邊個敢再提，又黎200萬人上街<br />\n本來就係一個會斷送政治生涯既炸彈<br />\n<br />\n講真<br />\n送中案未過，都重未有人因為送中案被送中<br />\n但黑警濫暴<br />\n被黑警拘捕，打傷，整盲，冤枉既香港人係確確實實，數不勝數<br />\n<br />\n如果一撤回條廢送中案<br />\n你地就收手<br />\n對得住為此而犧牲既手足們嗎？<br />\n而家收手即係將手足們都當係condom <br />\n黑警而家先係香港最大既亂源<br />\n一定要追求佢地到底<br />\n<br />\n黑警咁撚霸道<br />\n而家唔送中又點？<br />\n黑警都玩殘你啦，重洗送中咩？"},{"pid":"801c2d829a81762a524bf824e83a924ddaa22e09","tid":1538292,"uid":205394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:47:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aaae009556a06e6c3eb47897f2215f7d8017ac30","tid":1538292,"uid":266569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:48:18.000Z","msg":"我正式宣布香港人要6大訴求, 要加埋解散現役警隊及重組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533820</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5bd033d1a2034884772a6c4fcce097d7c891c218","tid":1538292,"uid":36920,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:49:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">黑警咁撚霸道<br />\n而家唔送中又點？<br />\n黑警都玩殘你啦，重洗送中咩？</span></span>"},{"pid":"058a258fc7ef2e62db62fa5769f13043642ec013","tid":1538292,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:50:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUGSMa3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUGSMa3.gif&h=1c74332a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【長期抗爭】最簡單有效嘅日常抗爭<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538155\" data-auto-link target=\"_bla